description: Triangle of number of (weakly) connected unlabeled digraphs with n nodes and k arcs (n >=2, k >= 1).
references: F. Harary and E. M. Palmer, Graphical Enumeration, Academic Press, NY, 1973.
example: [ 1,1 ],[ 0,3,4,4,1,1 ],[ 0,0,8,22,37,47,38,27,13,5,1,1 ][ the last batch giving the numbers of connected digraphs with 4 nodes and from 1 to 12 arcs ].
author: _Vladeta Jovovic_, Apr 21 2000
